{"tid":1865802,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺晚市嘅黃店少咗幾多人，希望大家多啲懲罰黃店！","createTime":"2020-02-06T11:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:43:06.000Z","uid":19501,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b29e5f57ca4243bbd7adcafd13bf1559f0972d5a","tid":1865802,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"幾個月前去食饗車仔麵，要排幾個字等位<br />\n今日同樣時間去食饗車仔麵，唔洗等直入，得10個8個客（之後先慢慢多客)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好忘記要keep住幫襯黃店，等黃店上救生艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhRJTXj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhRJTXj.png&h=e4130527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲客冇入鏡，並唔是一枱客都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEWJTYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEWJTYo.png&h=a867f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍店更加唔洗提，間間都等執咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f94070b41eedf3611859a318b1fb8bf9fd59a96","tid":1865802,"uid":253978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"無口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴豬咀去幫襯應該唔會被歧視"},{"pid":"6d77b067163fae35e944c3adf03501d173c60c56","tid":1865802,"uid":9825,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"依家肺炎咁勁 要食都賣外賣番屋企食算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ac840d0f3ea6acd907bfca3047950939278883","tid":1865802,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f94070b41eedf3611859a318b1fb8bf9fd59a96","tid":1865802,"uid":253978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"無口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴豬咀去幫